title: Thin Lizzy - Live at RockPalast (2-CD) 1981 ak320
description:
Thin Lizzy - Live at RockPalast (2-CD) 1981 ak320

Great line up of songs and Phil is at his best and the rest of the band is great.
This is another live masterpiece by Phil and the boys covering their older classics from Jailbreak to Chinatown, Renegade and Black Rose and Night Life.The band does a great live performance of Genocide from the Chinatown album. The sound quality on this is not bad.
And i must say that Snowy White did a great job on this effort.
(And he got around he also was on the Live Animals I just posted before this LOL)

Players

Phil Lynott – bass guitar, lead vocals (1969–83; died 1986)
Brian Downey – drums, percussion (1969–83, 1996–98, 2010–16)
Scott Gorham – guitar, backing vocals (1974–83, 1996–2001, 2004–)
Darren Wharton – keyboards, vocals (1981–83, 1996–2001, 2010–)
Snowy White – guitar, backing vocals (1980–82)
